@node Main "UkooBar - Documentation"

                              'UkooBar' 1.1

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'UkooBar' (pronounced "yoo-koo-barr"), is a Workbench @{" game " link play} where you
rotate bars between octagonal tiles to match various patterns. Complete
each of the 100 game patterns in the least amount of moves possible.

  Have fun!

               @{" Install and Play the game " link play}
               @{"   Features of the game    " link features}
